Package: mmequiv
Title: Calculate Standardized Morphine Milligram Equivalent Doses in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Kenneth A.", "Taylor", , "kenneth.taylor.dpt@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3205-9280"))
Description: Uses standardized methods to calculate morphine milligram equivalents (MME) for opioid dose comparison. The package includes API wrapper functions to call NIH HEAL MME Online Calulator and local functions that replicate the API's calculations on the user's local machine from the comfort of R.
License: GPL (>= 3) + file LICENSE
